org.springframework.data.tarantool.repository.config

Class TarantoolRepositoryOperationsMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.data.tarantool.repository.config.TarantoolRepositoryOperationsMapping

  • public class TarantoolRepositoryOperationsMapping
extends Object
    Holds mapping of TarantoolOperations to repositories and entities and allows to tell which implementation must be used for the specific domain entity.

      • resolve

        public TarantoolOperations resolve(Class<?> repositoryInterface,
                                   Class<?> entityClass)
        Given a repository interface and its domain type, resolves which TarantoolOperations should be used for them. The repository interface has the highest precedence and the entity class is lower. If no mapping is found, the default implementation will be returned.
        Parameters:
        repositoryInterface - repository interface to search the mapping by
        entityClass - domain entity class to search the mapping by
        Returns:
        TarantoolOperations instance

      • getMappingContext

        public org.springframework.data.mapping.context.MappingContext<? extends TarantoolPersistentEntity<?>,TarantoolPersistentProperty> getMappingContext()
        Get the MappingContext to use in repositories. It is extracted from the default TarantoolOperations.
        Returns:
        the mapping context.
